You realize JaGeX has a completed dragon kiteshield drop model, right? I stumbled upon it awhile ago, but it was practically 2d so I added some depth and a handle.

^Theres the worn model of it.

I spent maybe15-30 minutes trying to repair the halves before I found the full drop model.
Also, in case anyone wants, here’s the link to download them----->http://uppit.com/v/45TJIFW0
This is just the models in mqo form, if you want it in a server you’ll have to the rest on your own=P

-DKX
